Model:
* Independent of UI
* Data + logic
* The truth

ViewModel:
* Binds view to model
* Interpreter / gatekeeper

View:
* Reflects the model
* Stateless, declared, reactive

Option+click on something to read the docs for it (useful for jumping into color, font, etc)

command+option+enter to launch preview window

Anything that modifies self must label with `mutating`